data.description:
Cehck out this exceptional one-story home that exudes charm and functionality. 
Step inside this spacious home where every square foot is maximized to provide a sense versatility and comfort. The layout is a perfect balance between defined spaces and an airy ambiance, highlighted by the seamless mixture of the kitchen and family room, creating an inviting living space for all to enjoy. The home features plenty of bedrooms and bathrooms, ensuring privacy and comfort. Nestled within an expansive homesite and embraced by an open area, this residence offers tranquility and a versatile canvas for your backyard aspirations. Beyond what meets the eye, this home has a generous 2-car garage and convenient 4' side gate.
